  _missions:
  - Act: 1
    QuestId: firstForage
    Title: The First Forage
    Summary: Watch Wren enter the Edge Woods and gather safely.
  - Act: 2
    QuestId: edsGrandfather
    Title: Brightspore at the Bedside
    Summary: Ask Wren to help a grandfather who has stopped eating.
  - Act: 3
    QuestId: eddaApprentice
    Title: Edda Asks
    Summary: Ask to become Wren's formal apprentice.
  - Act: 3
    QuestId: festivalHosted
    Title: The First Festival in Three Years
    Summary: Help at the square and notice when Wren is hiding with dishes.
  _quotes:
  - Text: Grandfather hasn't eaten since Monday.
    Context: Asking Wren for help.
  - Text: That is not a big enough word.
    Context: Answering Wren after her grandfather eats a full bowl.
  - Text: Do not make me say the obvious part. I practiced the other part.
    Context: Making her apprenticeship request.
